# Bilibili Music Downloader

A command-line tool to download Bilibili videos and convert them to MP3 format, developed in **Python**.

[![Python](https://img.shields.io/badge/Python-3.7%2B-blue?logo=python)](https://www.python.org/)
[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-yellow.svg)](LICENSE)
![Status](https://img.shields.io/badge/Status-Stable-green)

## âœ¨ Features

- **ğŸ¶ Bilibili Video Search**: Search for videos on Bilibili by song name
- **ğŸ“¥ Video Download**: Download videos in MP4 format from Bilibili
- **ğŸµ Audio Conversion**: Convert downloaded videos to MP3 format using FFmpeg
- **âŒ¨ï¸ Interactive CLI**: User-friendly command-line interface with automatic selection
- **ğŸ“Š Progress Display**: Real-time download progress with rich progress bars

*Looking for the GUI version? It's in development and will be released soon!*

